**Dancer** | Townsfolk Power
__Basics__
The **dancer** may choose one player each night to roleblock. Roleblocked players are not able to perform any night actions. The **dancer** cannot roleblock the same player on consecutive nights. 

__Formalized__
Second Pre-End Night: Obstruct @Selection (~NextDay) [Quantity: %Number%, Succession: No Target Succession] |role_block.1|
